parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Failure due to Electrical Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause loss of power, stalling, and difficulty shifting gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission shifts gears independently
the vehicle stalls without warning
the transmission fails to shift out of park
the gear shifter fails to shift gears
the vehicle rolls back down a slope while in park.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Failure due to Mechanical Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause loss of power, stalling, and difficulty shifting gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission fails to shift out of third gear
the transmission revs to 8000 RPM
the vehicle loses power and can only be driven in second gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TCS can cause the vehicle to become disabled, leading to a safety hazard, especially in snowy or slippery conditions.
symptoms: The TCS kicks in and disables the vehicle
the vehicle is unable to move
the TVS light is on but the vehicle will not move.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the gear shifter can cause the vehicle to become stuck in park, leading to a safety hazard.
symptoms: The gear shifter fails to shift out of park
the gear shifter cap comes detached
the vehicle is stuck in park.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cooling system can cause the engine to overheat, leading to a potential fire hazard, engine damage, and stalling, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The temperature gauge rapidly increases to hot
the coolant level drops without warning
the engine overheats
the vehicle stalls
the coolant boils out of the reservoir
the engine oil and antifreeze mix together
a whining noise comes from the passenger side of the vehicle
the heater blows cool air.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and corrosion of the chassis can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle, affecting its safety and performance.
symptoms: Visible rust and corrosion on the chassis
potentially leading to weakened structural components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the door-ajar notification system can cause the doors to remain unlocked, even when the vehicle is turned off, posing a security risk.
symptoms: Random and intermittent illumination of the door-ajar notification light
doors failing to lock
even when the vehicle is turned off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexplained cracking of the windshield can obstruct the driver's view, posing a safety risk, and may require costly repairs.
symptoms: Large cracks appearing in the windshield without any apparent reason
potentially obstructing the driver's view.
